Hello I am Anna McLight and I live in London. I was born in 26th July 2003. I have a long straight blonde hair and pale skin. My eyes are big and blue and they are almond shape. I have a nice slim and curvy body and I do fitness that is why my body is so sexy. I study software engineer and i love programming.
To play tic tac toe I most pick a number that is from 1 to 9 and prevent you from getting sum of 15. I cant pick a number that has been picked. If I get 3 numbers whose sum is 15 I win.
